subject: Boxing
lead_paragraph: Ricky Hatton’s first fight in more than three years ended in disappointment: the Ukrainian welterweight Vyacheslav Senchenko stopped him in the ninth round in a nontitle fight in Hatton’s home city, Manchester, England.
